title_japanese: Sランクパーティから解雇された【呪具師】～『呪いのアイテム』しか作れませんが、その性能はアーティファクト級なり……！～
title_synonyms: My S-Rank Party Fired Me for Being a Cursificer: I Can Only Make "Cursed Items," but They're Artifact Class!
synopsis:
Gail Hamilton is a "curse crafter" who got booted from his party for allegedly not pulling his weight...right after they were promoted to the Guild's "S" rank. Unfortunately, the party didn't realize that Gail's cursed goods pack the power of holy relics and legendary gear! But too bad for them, because Gail's going it alone now...and causing a sensation with the creepy-yet-useful curses he works with!

(Source: Kodansha USA)
background: S-Rank Party kara Kaiko sareta "Jugushi": "Noroi no Item" shika Tsukuremasen ga, Sono Seinou wa Artifact-kyuu nari......! has been published digitally in English as I'm a Curse Crafter, and I Don't Need an S-Rank Party! by Kodansha USA through K Manga.
